{"id":133439,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/01/视频：加拿大卡车失控的惊险镜头/","date":"2011-01-23T22:40:31Z","modified":"2011-01-23T22:40:31Z","title":"视频：加拿大卡车失控的惊险镜头","content":"<div>\n<p>加拿大的一名司机用车头的监控镜头拍下了这个惊险场面。</p>\n<p>克里斯尚于星期五（1月21日）开车到安大略省圭尔夫附近时，行驶在高速公路相反方向上的一辆卡车突然失控，撞跨了分隔带，几乎就要把克里斯尚的车子撞倒。</p>\n<p>克里斯尚刚好来得及闪避，事故中也没有人受重伤，卡车的司机则被起诉不小心驾驶罪。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wVvP3rVUZLcxrJAAUN1dRQ7xanw/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wVvP3rVUZLcxrJAAUN1dRQ7xanw/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wVvP3rVUZLcxrJAAUN1dRQ7xanw/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wVvP3rVUZLcxrJAAUN1dRQ7xanw/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=vNMkXJv7clY:rOzug9V7dBQ:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=vNMkXJv7clY:rOzug9V7dBQ:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=vNMkXJv7clY:rOzug9V7dBQ:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=vNMkXJv7clY:rOzug9V7dBQ:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=vNMkXJv7clY:rOzug9V7dBQ:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=vNMkXJv7clY:rOzug9V7dBQ:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/vNMkXJv7clY\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<h4>要翻墙? <a href=\"http://898989.biz\">用赛风</a>.</h4>\n","author":176,"c